European Club Association chairman Andrea Agnelli confirmed on Tuesday that the continent&rsquo;s biggest sides and UEFA have agreed to pay back a total of &pound;519m to its broadcast partners. <br />
<br />
Agnelli: &ldquo;We are looking at top revenue decrease of approximately &euro;4bn in the next 2 years&rdquo;

